rosas.lou.calculator
Class RunDistance

java.lang.Object
  rosas.lou.calculator.RunDistance
public class RunDistance
extends java.lang.Object

RunDistance Class by Lou Rosas This class encapsulates the distance data used by the Pace Calculator. It stores the units: Miles, Kilometers and Meters and the value.
